<%- include('../../partials/header') %>

<body>
  <div class="form-container">
    <div class="form-card">
      <div class="form-card-body">
        <h2 class="form-title">Create a S.M.A.R.T. Goal</h2>
        <p class="form-description">
          The first step toward self-improvement and becoming your best self is setting a <strong>S.M.A.R.T.</strong> goal.
          S.M.A.R.T. stands for <em>Specific, Measurable, Achievable, Relevant, and Time-Bound</em>.
          <br><br>
          I'll guide you through creating your first one. Let's begin with the first step: <strong>Specific</strong>.
          <br><br>
          Do you want your first goal to focus on improving your <strong>mind</strong> or your <strong>body</strong>?
          (Don't worry if you have goals for both â€” you can always create more later!)
        </p>

        <form action="/user" method="POST" class="goal-form">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="name" class="form-label">Name your goal (be Specific but concise):</label>
            <input type="text" name="name" id="name" class="form-input" placeholder="e.g., Lose 10lbs, Learn Spanish" required>
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="Type" class="form-label">Goal type:</label>
            <select id="Type" name="Type" class="form-select" required>
              <option value="mind" selected>Mind</option>
              <option value="body">Body</option>
            </select>
          </div>

          <button type="submit" class="submit-button">Add New Goal</button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

